Description: Fix HDF5 high-level header selection for HDF5 2.x
 HDF5 2.1.0 has a lower minor version than HDF5 1.14.x, so checking
 only H5_VERS_MINOR incorrectly selects the legacy HDF5 1.6 header path.
Author: Gilles Filippini <pini@debian.org>
Forwarded: not-needed
Last-Update: 2026-06-10

--- a/src/libstfio/hdf5/hdf5lib.cpp
+++ b/src/libstfio/hdf5/hdf5lib.cpp
@@ -13,7 +13,7 @@
 // Foundation, Inc., 51 Franklin Street, Fifth Floor, Boston, MA  02110-1301, USA.
 
 #include "hdf5.h"
-#if H5_VERS_MINOR > 6
+#if H5_VERS_MAJOR > 1 || H5_VERS_MINOR > 6
   #include "hdf5_hl.h"
 #else
   #include "H5TA.h"
